text: Arif Dwi Pangestu is an Indonesian archer. He was born on 25 March 2004. Dwi Pangestu competed at the 2020 Summer Olympics.Arif Dwi PangestuArif DWI PANGESTU == References == Category:2004 births Category:Living people Category:Indonesian archers Category:Olympians for Indonesia
